# Smart Vision Bot - Environment Configuration
# Copy this file to .env and add your API keys

# ========================================
# LLM API Keys (Choose one or more)
# ========================================

# Groq API (Recommended - Fast & Free)
# Get key from: https://console.groq.com/
GROQ_API_KEY=*********

# Google AI Studio (Free tier available)
# Get key from: https://makersuite.google.com/
GOOGLE_API_KEY=*********

# ========================================
# News API Keys (Optional - Choose one)
# ========================================

GNEWS_API_KEY=*********

# NewsData.io (200 requests/day free)
# Get key from: https://newsdata.io/
NEWSDATA_API_KEY=*********

# Currents API (600 requests/month free)
# Get key from: https://currentsapi.services/
CURRENTS_API_KEY=*********

# ========================================
# System Configuration (Optional)
# ========================================

# Camera settings
# CAMERA_INDEX=0
# CAMERA_WIDTH=640
# CAMERA_HEIGHT=480

# Face recognition settings  
# FACE_RECOGNITION_TOLERANCE=0.6
# FACE_DETECTION_CONFIDENCE=0.7

# TTS settings
# TTS_RATE=180
# TTS_VOLUME=0.9

# ========================================
# Instructions:
# ========================================
# 1. Copy this file to .env (remove .example)
# 2. Uncomment the lines you want to use (remove #)
# 3. Replace 'your_key_here' with your actual API keys
# 4. Save the file
# 5. Run the application with: python app.py
#
# Note: The bot will work without API keys but with limited functionality
# Weather API (Open-Meteo) requires no key and works out of the box!
